text: 1\. SSK 1919 is a football club from Salzburg. It was founded 1919 and is the second oldest football club in Salzburg. ==History== The club was founded by the former Vienna player Hans Dobesch. They played mostly in the highest levels of Salzburg. The biggest success was reaching the Austrian cup semifinal in the 1947/48 season.
